title: Completeness of death registration with cause-of-death information (%)
name: sp.reg.dths.zs
readme: Completeness of death registration is the estimated percentage of deaths that are registered with their cause of death information in the vital registration system of a country.

fields.name: Country Code
fields.description: ISO 3-digit ISO code extended to include regional codes e.g. EUR, ARB etc

fields.name: Value
fields.description: Completeness of death registration is the estimated percentage of deaths that are registered with their cause of death information in the vital registration system of a country.
